ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Whether this healthcareservice record is in active use.

ivardefs.name: appointmentRequired
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether or not a prospective consumer will require an appointment for a particular service at a site to be provided by the Organization. Indicates if an appointment is required for access to this service.

ivardefs.name: availabilityExceptions
ivardefs.desc: A description of site availability exceptions, e.g. public holiday availability. Succinctly describing all possible exceptions to normal site availability as details in the available Times and not available Times.

ivardefs.name: availableTime_
ivardefs.desc: A collection of times that the Service Site is available.

ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the broad category of service being performed or delivered.

ivardefs.name: characteristic_
ivardefs.desc: Collection of characteristics (attributes).

ivardefs.name: comment
ivardefs.desc: Any additional description of the service and/or any specific issues not covered by the other attributes, which can be displayed as further detail under the serviceName.

ivardefs.name: coverageArea_
ivardefs.desc: The location(s) that this service is available to (not where the service is provided).

ivardefs.name: eligibility
ivardefs.desc: Does this service have specific eligibility requirements that need to be met in order to use the service?

ivardefs.name: eligibilityNote
ivardefs.desc: Describes the eligibility conditions for the service.

ivardefs.name: endpoint_
ivardefs.desc: Technical endpoints providing access to services operated for the specific healthcare services defined at this resource.

ivardefs.name: extraDetails
ivardefs.desc: Extra details about the service that can't be placed in the other fields.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: External identifiers for this item.

ivardefs.name: location_
ivardefs.desc: The location(s) where this healthcare service may be provided.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: Further description of the service as it would be presented to a consumer while searching.

ivardefs.name: notAvailable_
ivardefs.desc: The HealthcareService is not available during this period of time due to the provided reason.

ivardefs.name: photo
ivardefs.desc: If there is a photo/symbol associated with this HealthcareService, it may be included here to facilitate quick identification of the service in a list.

ivardefs.name: programName_
ivardefs.desc: Program Names that can be used to categorize the service.

ivardefs.name: providedBy
ivardefs.desc: The organization that provides this healthcare service.

ivardefs.name: referralMethod_
ivardefs.desc: Ways that the service accepts referrals, if this is not provided then it is implied that no referral is required.

ivardefs.name: serviceProvisionCode_
ivardefs.desc: The code(s) that detail the conditions under which the healthcare service is available/offered.

ivardefs.name: specialty_
ivardefs.desc: Collection of specialties handled by the service site. This is more of a medical term.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: List of contacts related to this specific healthcare service.

ivardefs.name: type_
ivardefs.desc: The specific type of service that may be delivered or performed.
